title: Ulta Beauty: 12-Piece Spring Beauty Bag ONLY $12.99 ($88 Value!)
text:
$88 worth of makeup for just $12.99? Yes please! For a limited time and while supplies last, you can head to your local Ulta Beauty store where they are offering up their Spring 2017 Beauty Bags for just $12.99 (an $88 value)! Each 12-piece kit comes in either a peach or blue bag and includes a brow tint, eye primer, dual ended eye liner, mascara, eye shadow palette, pencil sharpener, blush brush, makeup remover pads, highlighter duo palette, lip stick, and a lip gloss stain!

Also included is a coupon for $5 off any Ulta Beauty Collection cosmetic or brush purchase of $15 or more – valid in store or online 3/12/17 through 5/27/17. What a sweet deal!

Grab a Discounted Ulta eGift Card! Hop on over to eBay where you can grab a $100 Ulta eGift Card for ONLY $90 ! Your gift card will be emailed to you within 24 hours. Grabbing discounted Ulta gift cards is a great way to save on rarely discounted high-end cosmetic brands.
Be Sure to Check out Ulta’s 21 Days of Beauty Steals!
